#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the cursor position to <replaceable>line</replaceable> and "
"<replaceable>column</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"कर्सरस्थानं <replaceable>line</replaceable> तथा <replaceable>column</"
"replaceable> इति सेट् करोति ।"

