"एतस्य कर्सरस्य तुलनां कर्सरस्य <replaceable>other</replaceable> इत्यनेन सह करोति । "
"प्रत्यागच्छति"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2753
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>-1</literal>, if this cursor is located before the cursor "
"<replaceable>other</replaceable>,"
msgstr ""
"<literal>-1</literal>, यदि एषः कर्सरः <replaceable>other</replaceable> कर्सरस्य "
"पुरतः स्थितः अस्ति,"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2754
#, no-c-format
msgid "<literal>0</literal>, if both cursors equal and"
msgstr "<literal>0</literal>, यदि उभौ कर्सरौ समानौ तथा च"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2755
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>+1</literal>, if this cursor is located after the cursor "
"<replaceable>other</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>+1</literal>, यदि एषः कर्सरः कर्सरस्य <replaceable>other</replaceable> "
"इत्यस्य पश्चात् स्थितः अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2762
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool Cursor.equals(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>other</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool Cursor.equals(<पैरामीटर>कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय>अन्य</प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2763
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if this cursor and the cursor "
"<replaceable>other</replaceable> are equal, otherwise <literal>false</"
"literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> इति प्रत्यागच्छति, यदि अयं कर्सरः <replaceable>other</"
"replaceable> च समानौ स्तः, अन्यथा <literal>false</literal> ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2771
#, no-c-format
msgid "String Cursor.toString();"
msgstr "स्ट्रिंग कर्सर.toString ();"

