"कन्स्ट्रक्टर् । <literal>new Range(<replaceable>startLine</replaceable>, "
"<replaceable>startColumn</replaceable>, <replaceable>endLine</replaceable>, "
"<replaceable>endColumn</replaceable>)</literal> इति आह्वयन् Range प्रत्यागच्छति "
"(<replaceable>startLine</replaceable>, <replaceable>startColumn</"
"replaceable>) तः (<replaceable>endLine</replaceable>, "
"<replaceable>endColumn</replaceable>) इति ।"

