#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool Range.containsLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool Range.containsLine(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2885
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if <replaceable>line</replaceable> is in "
"the half open interval <literal>[start.line, end.line)</literal>, otherwise "
"<literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> इति प्रेषयति, यदि <replaceable>line</replaceable> "
"अर्धमुक्तान्तरे <literal>[start.line, end.line)</literal> अस्ति, अन्यथा "
"<literal>false</literal> >।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2893
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool Range.overlaps(<parameter>Range <replaceable>other</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool Range.overlaps(<पैरामीटर>परिधि <प्रतिस्थापनीय>अन्य</प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2894
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if this range and the range "
"<replaceable>other</replaceable> share a common region, otherwise "
"<literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> इति प्रत्यागच्छति, यदि एषा परिधिः <replaceable>other</"
"replaceable> इति परिधिः च सामान्यप्रदेशं साझां कुर्वन्ति, अन्यथा <literal>false</"
"literal> ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2902
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool Range.overlapsLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool Range.overlapsLine(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2903
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if <replaceable>line</replaceable> is in "
"the interval <literal>[start.line, end.line]</literal>, otherwise "
"<literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> इति प्रत्यागच्छति, यदि <replaceable>line</replaceable> "
"<literal>[start.line, end.line]</literal> इति अन्तरे अस्ति, अन्यथा "
"<literal>false</literal> ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2911
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool Range.overlapsColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool Range.overlapsColumn (<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>स्तम्भ</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2912
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if <replaceable>column</replaceable> is in "
"the interval <literal>[start.column, end.column]</literal>, otherwise "
"<literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> इति प्रत्यागच्छति, यदि <replaceable>column</"
"replaceable> <literal>[start.column, end.column]</literal> इति अन्तरे अस्ति, "
"अन्यथा <literal>false</literal> ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2920
#, no-c-format
msgid "bool Range.onSingleLine();"
msgstr "bool श्रेणी.onSingleLine ();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2921
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the range starts and ends at the same "
"line, &ie; if <replaceable>Range.start.line == Range.end.line</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> इति प्रेषयति, यदि परिधिः समानरेखायां आरभ्यते समाप्तं च भवति, "
"&ie; if <replaceable>Range.start.line == परिधि.अन्त.रेखा</replaceable>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2925 development.docbook:3359 development.docbook:3498
#, no-c-format
msgid "Since: &kde; 4.9"
msgstr "यतः: &where; ४.९"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2932
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool Range.equals(<parameter>Range <replaceable>other</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool Range.equals(<पैरामीटर>परिधि <प्रतिस्थापनीय>अन्य</प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2933
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if this range and the Range "
"<replaceable>other</replaceable> are equal, otherwise <literal>false</"
"literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> इति प्रत्यागच्छति, यदि एषा परिधिः <replaceable>other</"
"replaceable> च समानौ स्तः, अन्यथा <literal>false</literal> ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2941
#, no-c-format
msgid "String Range.toString();"
msgstr "स्ट्रिंग रेंज.toString ();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2942
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the range as a string of the form <quote><literal>Range(Cursor(line, "
"column), Cursor(line, column))</literal></quote>."
msgstr ""
"<quote><literal>Range(Cursor(line, column), Cursor(line, column))</literal></"
"quote> इति रूपस्य स्ट्रिंग् रूपेण श्रेणीं प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

