msgid ""
"String read(<parameter>String <replaceable>file</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String read(<पैरामीटर>स्ट्रिंग <प्रतिस्थापनीय>सञ्चिका</प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2960
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Will search the given <replaceable>file</replaceable> relative to the "
"<literal>katepart5/script/files</literal> directory and return its content "
"as a string."
msgstr ""
"<literal>katepart5/script/files</literal> निर्देशिकायाः सापेक्षं दत्तं "
"<replaceable>file</replaceable> अन्वेषयिष्यति, तस्य सामग्रीं च स्ट्रिंग् रूपेण "
"प्रत्यागमिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2966
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void require(<parameter>String <replaceable>file</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"void require(<पैरामीटर>स्ट्रिंग <प्रतिस्थापनीय>सञ्चिका</प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2967
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Will search the given <replaceable>file</replaceable> relative to the "
"<literal>katepart5/script/libraries</literal> directory and evaluate it. "
"<literal>require</literal> is internally guarded against multiple inclusions "
"of the same <replaceable>file</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>katepart5/script/libraries</literal> निर्देशिकायाः सापेक्षं दत्तां "
"<replaceable>सञ्चिकां</replaceable> अन्वेषयिष्यति, तस्य मूल्याङ्कनं च करिष्यति । "
"<literal>require</literal> इत्यस्य आन्तरिकरूपेण एकस्यामेव <replaceable>सञ्चिकायाः</"
"replaceable> इत्यस्य बहुविधसमावेशानां रक्षणं भवति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2971
#, no-c-format
msgid "Since: &kde; 4.10"
msgstr "यतः: &where; ४.१०"

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:2980
#, no-c-format
msgid "Debugging"
msgstr "त्रुटिनिवारणम्"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2983
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void debug(<parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr "void debug(<पैरामीटर>स्ट्रिंग <प्रतिस्थापनीय>पाठ</प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2984
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Prints <replaceable>text</replaceable> to <literal>stdout</literal> in the "
"console launching the application."
msgstr ""
"अनुप्रयोगं प्रारभमाणे कन्सोल् मध्ये <replaceable>text</replaceable> इत्येतत् "
"<literal>stdout</literal> इत्यत्र मुद्रयति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:2993
#, no-c-format
msgid "Translation"
msgstr "अनुवाद"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2995
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In order to support full localization, there are several functions to "
"translate strings in scripts, namely <literal>i18n</literal>, "
"<literal>i18nc</literal>, <literal>i18np</literal> and <literal>i18ncp</"
"literal>. These functions behave exactly like <ulink url=\"https://techbase."
"kde.org/Development/Tutorials/Localization/i18n\"> &kde;'s translation "
"functions</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"पूर्णस्थानीयकरणस्य समर्थनार्थं स्क्रिप्ट्-मध्ये स्ट्रिंग्-अनुवादं कर्तुं अनेकाः कार्याणि सन्ति, यथा "
"<literal>i18n</literal>, <literal>i18nc</literal>, <literal>i18np</literal> "
"तथा <literal>i18ncp< /शाब्दिक>। एतानि कार्याणि <ulink url=\"https://techbase."
"kde.org/Development/Tutorials/Localization/i18n\"> &kde; इत्यस्य अनुवादकार्यं</"
"ulink> इव एव वर्तन्ते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3002
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The translation functions translate the wrapped strings through &kde;'s "
"translation system to the language used in the application. Strings in "
"scripts being developed in the official &kappname; sources are automatically "
"extracted and translatable. In other words, as a &kappname; developer you do "
"not have to bother with message extraction and translation. It should be "
"noted though, that the translation only works inside the &kde; "
"infrastructure, &ie;, new strings in 3rd-party scripts developed outside of "
"&kde; are not translated. Therefore, please consider contributing your "
"scripts to &kate; such that proper translation is possible."
msgstr ""
"अनुवादकार्यं &kde;इत्यस्य अनुवादप्रणाल्याः माध्यमेन लपेटितानां तारानाम् अनुवादं अनुप्रयोगे "
"प्रयुक्तभाषायां करोति । आधिकारिक &kappname; स्रोताः स्वयमेव निष्कासिताः अनुवादयोग्याः "
"च भवन्ति । अन्येषु शब्देषु यथा &कप्पनाम; developer भवद्भिः सन्देशनिष्कासनेन अनुवादेन च कष्टं "
"न कर्तव्यम्। तथापि ज्ञातव्यं यत् अनुवादः केवलं &kde; infrastructure, &ie;, &kde; न "
"अनुवादिताः भवन्ति। अतः कृपया स्वलिपिनां योगदानं &kate; यथा सम्यक् अनुवादः सम्भवति।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3014
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void i18n(<parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<replaceable>arg1</replaceable>, ...);"
msgstr ""
"void i18n(<पैरामीटर>स्ट्रिंग <प्रतिस्थापनीय>पाठ</प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>, "
"<प्रतिस्थापनीय>arg1</प्रतिस्थापनीय>, ...);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3015
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Translates <replaceable>text</replaceable> into the language used by the "
"application. The arguments <replaceable>arg1</replaceable>, ..., are "
"optional and used to replace the placeholders <literal>%1</literal>, "
"<literal>%2</literal>, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"अनुप्रयोगेन प्रयुक्तभाषायां <replaceable>text</replaceable> इति अनुवादयति । "
"<replaceable>arg1</replaceable>, ..., इति तर्काः वैकल्पिकाः सन्ति, <literal>%1</"
"literal>, <literal>%2</literal>, &etc;"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3022
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void i18nc(<parameter>String <replaceable>context</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<replaceable>arg1</replaceable>, ...);"
msgstr ""
"void i18nc(<पैरामीटर>स्ट्रिंग <प्रतिस्थापनीय>सन्दर्भ</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<पैरामीटर>स्ट्रिंग <प्रतिस्थापनीय>पाठ</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<प्रतिस्थापनीय>arg1</replaceable>, ...) ;"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3023
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Translates <replaceable>text</replaceable> into the language used by the "
"application. Additionally, the string <replaceable>context</replaceable> is "
"visible to translators so they can provide a better translation. The "
"arguments <replaceable>arg1</replaceable>, ..., are optional and used to "
"replace the placeholders <literal>%1</literal>, <literal>%2</literal>, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"अनुप्रयोगेन प्रयुक्तायां भाषायां <replaceable>text</replaceable> इति अनुवादयति । "
"तदतिरिक्तं <replaceable>context</replaceable> इति स्ट्रिंग् अनुवादकानां कृते दृश्यते अतः "
"ते उत्तमं अनुवादं दातुं शक्नुवन्ति । <replaceable>arg1</replaceable>, ..., इति तर्काः "
"वैकल्पिकाः सन्ति, <literal>%1</literal>, <literal>%2</literal>, &etc;"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3032
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void i18np(<parameter>String <replaceable>singular</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>plural</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>number</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<replaceable>arg1</replaceable>, ...);"
msgstr ""
"void i18np(<parameter>String <replaceable>एकवचन</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>String <replaceable>बहुवचन</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>संख्या</replaceable>< /पैरामीटर>, "
"<प्रतिस्थापनीय>arg1</प्रतिस्थापनीय>, ...);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3033
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Translates either <replaceable>singular</replaceable> or "
"<replaceable>plural</replaceable> into the language used by the application, "
"depending on the given <replaceable>number</replaceable>. The arguments "
"<replaceable>arg1</replaceable>, ..., are optional and used to replace the "
"placeholders <literal>%1</literal>, <literal>%2</literal>, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"दत्तस्य <replaceable>सङ्ख्या</replaceable> इत्यस्य आधारेण अनुप्रयोगेन प्रयुक्तभाषायां "
"<replaceable>एकवचनं</replaceable> अथवा <replaceable>plural</replaceable> इति "
"अनुवादयति । <replaceable>arg1</replaceable>, ..., इति तर्काः वैकल्पिकाः सन्ति, "
"<literal>%1</literal>, <literal>%2</literal>, &etc;"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3042
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void i18ncp(<parameter>String <replaceable>context</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>singular</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>plural</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>number</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<replaceable>arg1</replaceable>, ...);"
msgstr ""
"void i18ncp(<पैरामीटर>स्ट्रिंग <प्रतिस्थापनीय>सन्दर्भ</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<पैरामीटर>स्ट्रिंग <प्रतिस्थापनीय>एकवचन</replaceable></parameter>, <पैरामीटर>स्ट्रिंग "
"<प्रतिस्थापनीय>बहुवचन</replaceable>< /parameter>, <parameter>int "
"<प्रतिस्थापनीय>संख्या</replaceable></parameter>, <प्रतिस्थापनीय>arg1</"
"replaceable>, ...);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3043
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Translates either <replaceable>singular</replaceable> or "
"<replaceable>plural</replaceable> into the language used by the application, "
"depending on the given <replaceable>number</replaceable>. Additionally, the "
"string <replaceable>context</replaceable> is visible to translators so they "
"can provide a better translation. The arguments <replaceable>arg1</"
"replaceable>, ..., are optional and used to replace the placeholders "
"<literal>%1</literal>, <literal>%2</literal>, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"दत्तस्य <replaceable>सङ्ख्या</replaceable> इत्यस्य आधारेण अनुप्रयोगेन प्रयुक्तभाषायां "
"<replaceable>एकवचनं</replaceable> अथवा <replaceable>plural</replaceable> इति "
"अनुवादयति । तदतिरिक्तं <replaceable>context</replaceable> इति स्ट्रिंग् अनुवादकानां "
"कृते दृश्यते अतः ते उत्तमं अनुवादं दातुं शक्नुवन्ति । <replaceable>arg1</replaceable>, ..., "
"इति तर्काः वैकल्पिकाः सन्ति, <literal>%1</literal>, <literal>%2</literal>, &etc;"

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:3057
#, no-c-format
msgid "The View API"
msgstr "दृश्य एपिआइ इति"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3058
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whenever a script is being executed, there is a global variable "
"<quote><literal>view</literal></quote> representing the current active "
"editor view. The following is a list of all available View functions."
msgstr ""
"यदा कदापि स्क्रिप्ट् निष्पादितं भवति तदा वर्तमानसक्रियसम्पादकदृश्यस्य प्रतिनिधित्वं कुर्वन् "
"वैश्विकचरः <quote><literal>view</literal></quote> भवति । निम्नलिखितम् सर्वेषां "
"उपलब्धानां View कार्याणां सूची अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3065
#, no-c-format
msgid "<function>void view.copy()</function>"
msgstr "<function>void view.copy()</function> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3067
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copy the selection if there is one, otherwise the current line if the option "
"<userinput>[ ] Copy/Cut the current line if no selection</userinput> is set."
msgstr ""
"यदि एकः अस्ति तर्हि चयनं प्रतिलिख्यताम्, अन्यथा वर्तमानपङ्क्तिं यदि विकल्पः "
"<userinput>[ ] वर्तमानपङ्क्तिं प्रतिलिख्य/कटयतु यदि कोऽपि चयनः</userinput> सेट् न "
"भवति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3068 development.docbook:3077 development.docbook:3086
#, no-c-format
msgid "Since: &kde-frameworks; 5.79"
msgstr "यतः: &kde-frameworks; ५.७९ इति"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3074
#, no-c-format
msgid "<function>void view.cut()</function>"
msgstr "<function>void view.cut()</function> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3076
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Cut the selection if there is one, otherwise the current line if the option "
"<userinput>[ ] Copy/Cut the current line if no selection</userinput> is set."
msgstr ""
"यदि एकः अस्ति तर्हि चयनं कटयन्तु, अन्यथा वर्तमानपङ्क्तिं यदि विकल्पः <userinput>[ ] "
"वर्तमानपङ्क्तिं प्रतिलिख्य/कटयतु यदि कोऽपि चयनः</userinput> सेट् न भवति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3083
#, no-c-format
msgid "<function>void view.paste()</function>"
msgstr "<function>void view.paste()</function> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3085
#, no-c-format
msgid "Paste the clipboard content."
msgstr "क्लिपबोर्ड सामग्रीं चिनोतु।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3092
#, no-c-format
msgid "<function>Cursor view.cursorPosition()</function>"
msgstr "<function>कर्सर view.cursorPosition()</function> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3093
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the current cursor position in the view."
msgstr "दृश्ये वर्तमानं कर्सरस्थानं प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3098
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void view.setCursorPosition(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"void view.setCursorPosition(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"void view.setCursorPosition(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>, <पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>स्तम्भ</प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);\n"
"void view.setCursorPosition (<पैरामीटर> कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय> कर्सर</"
"प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3099
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the current cursor position to either (line, column) or to the given "
"cursor."
msgstr "वर्तमानं कर्सरस्थानं (रेखा, स्तम्भ) अथवा दत्तकर्सर इत्यत्र सेट् कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3106
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cursor view.virtualCursorPosition();"
msgstr "कर्सर view.virtualCursorPosition ();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the virtual cursor position with each tab counting the corresponding "
"amount of spaces depending on the current tab width."
msgstr ""
"वर्तमान ट्याब् विस्तारस्य आधारेण प्रत्येकं ट्याब् तत्सम्बद्धानि रिक्तस्थानानि गणयन् वर्चुअल् "
"कर्सरस्थानं प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void view.setVirtualCursorPosition(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"void view.setVirtualCursorPosition(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"void view.setVirtualCursorPosition(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</"
"replaceable></पैरामीटर>, <पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>स्तम्भ</replaceable></"
"पैरामीटर>);\n"
"void view.setVirtualCursorPosition (<पैरामीटर> कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय> कर्सर</"
"प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the current virtual cursor position to (line, column) or to the given "
"cursor."
msgstr "वर्तमान वर्चुअल् कर्सरस्थानं (रेखा, स्तम्भ) अथवा दत्तकर्सर इत्यत्र सेट् कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3122
#, no-c-format
msgid "String view.selectedText();"
msgstr "स्ट्रिंग view.selectedText ();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the selected text. If no text is selected, the returned string is "
"empty."
msgstr ""
"चयनितं पाठं प्रत्यागच्छति । यदि कोऽपि पाठः न चिनोति तर्हि प्रत्यागतं स्ट्रिंग् रिक्तं भवति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3130
#, no-c-format
msgid "bool view.hasSelection();"
msgstr "bool view.hasचयन ();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the view has selected text, otherwise "
"<literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> इति प्रत्यागच्छति, यदि दृश्येन पाठः चयनितः अस्ति, अन्यथा "
"<literal>false</literal> ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3138
#, no-c-format
msgid "Range view.selection();"
msgstr "श्रेणी दृश्य.चयन ();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the selected text range. The returned range is invalid if there is "
"no selected text."
msgstr ""
"चयनितं पाठपरिधिं प्रत्यागच्छति । यदि चयनितः पाठः नास्ति तर्हि प्रत्यागतः परिधिः "
"अमान्यः भवति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void view.setSelection(<parameter>Range <replaceable>range</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"void view.setSelection (<पैरामीटर>परिधि <प्रतिस्थापनीय>परिधि</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3148
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the selected text to the given range."
msgstr "चयनितं पाठं दत्तपरिधिं प्रति सेट् कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3155
#, no-c-format
msgid "void view.removeSelectedText();"
msgstr "void view.removeचयनित पाठ ();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Remove the selected text. If the view does not have any selected text, this "
"does nothing."
msgstr ""
"चयनितं पाठं निष्कासयन्तु। यदि दृश्ये कोऽपि चयनितः पाठः नास्ति तर्हि एतेन किमपि न भवति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3164
#, no-c-format
msgid "void view.selectAll();"
msgstr "void view.selectAll ();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3165
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selects the entire text in the document."
msgstr "दस्तावेजे सम्पूर्णं पाठं चिनोति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3172
#, no-c-format
msgid "void view.clearSelection();"
msgstr "void view.clearचयन ();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Clears the text selection without removing the text."
msgstr "पाठं न निष्कास्य पाठचयनं स्वच्छं करोति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3180
#, no-c-format
msgid "void view.setBlockSelection(bool on);"
msgstr "void view.setBlockSelection (bool पर);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3181
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set block selection mode on or off."
msgstr "ब्लॉकचयनविधिं चालू वा निष्क्रियं वा सेट् कुर्वन्तु।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3187
#, no-c-format
msgid "bool view.blockSelection();"
msgstr "bool view.blockचयन ();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if block selection mode is on, otherwise "
"<literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> इति प्रत्यागच्छति, यदि ब्लॉकचयनविधिः चालू अस्ति, अन्यथा "
"<literal>false</literal> ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void view.align(<parameter>Range <replaceable>range</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"void view.align(<पैरामीटर>परिधि <प्रतिस्थापनीय>परिधि</प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Properly re-indent lines within <replaceable>range</replaceable> according "
"to current indentation settings."
msgstr ""
"वर्तमान इण्डेन्टेशन सेटिंग्स् इत्यस्य अनुसारं <replaceable>range</replaceable> इत्यस्य अन्तः "
"रेखाः सम्यक् पुनः इन्डेण्ट् कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void view.alignOn(<parameter>Range <replaceable>range</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>pattern</replaceable> = &quot;"
"&quot;</parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"void view.alignOn(<पैरामीटर>परिधि <प्रतिस्थापनीय>परिधि</प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>, "
"<पैरामीटर>स्ट्रिंग <प्रतिस्थापनीय>प्रतिमान</प्रतिस्थापनीय> = &quot;&quot;</पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Aligns lines in <replaceable>range</replaceable> on the column given by the "
"regular expression <replaceable>pattern</replaceable>. With an empty "
"<replaceable>pattern</replaceable> it will align on the first non-blank "
"character by default. If the pattern has a capture it will indent on the "
"captured match."
msgstr ""
"नियमितव्यञ्जनेन <replaceable>pattern</replaceable> इत्यनेन दत्ते स्तम्भे "
"<replaceable>range</replaceable> इत्यत्र रेखाः संरेखयति । रिक्तेन "
"<replaceable>pattern</replaceable> इत्यनेन सह पूर्वनिर्धारितरूपेण प्रथमे अरिक्तवर्णे "
"संरेखयिष्यति । यदि प्रतिरूपस्य ग्रहणं भवति तर्हि सः गृहीतमेलने इन्डेण्ट् करिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: development.docbook:3209
#, no-c-format
msgid "Examples:"
msgstr "उदाहरणानि :"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>view.alignOn(document.documentRange(), '-');</literal> will insert "
"spaces before the first <literal>-</literal> of each lines to align them all "
"on the same column."
msgstr ""
"<literal>view.alignOn(document.documentRange(), '-');</literal> प्रत्येकस्य "
"पङ्क्तेः प्रथमस्य <literal>-</literal> इत्यस्य पूर्वं रिक्तस्थानानि निवेशयिष्यति यत् तान् "
"सर्वान् एकस्मिन् स्तम्भे संरेखयिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>view.alignOn(document.documentRange(), ':\\\\s+(.)');</literal> "
"will insert spaces before the first non-blank character that occurs after a "
"colon to align them all on the same column."
msgstr ""
"<literal>view.alignOn(document.documentRange(), ':\\\\s+(.)');</literal> "
"सर्वान् एकस्मिन् एव संरेखयितुं कोलनस्य अनन्तरं भवति इति प्रथमस्य अ-रिक्तवर्णस्य पूर्वं "
"रिक्तस्थानानि सम्मिलितं करिष्यति स्तम्भ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"object view.executeCommand(<parameter>String <replaceable>command</"
"replaceable></parameter>,\n"
"                           <parameter>String <replaceable>args</"
"replaceable></parameter>,\n"
"                           <parameter>Range <replaceable>range</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"object view.executeCommand(<पैरामीटर>स्ट्रिंग <प्रतिस्थापनीय>आदेश</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>,\n"
"                           <parameter>स्ट्रिंग् <replaceable>args</replaceable></"
"parameter>, 1.1.\n"
"                           <parameter>परिधि <प्रतिस्थापनीय>परिधि</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3217
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Executes the <link linkend=\"advanced-editing-tools-commandline\">command "
"line command</link> <replaceable>command</replaceable> with the optional "
"arguments <replaceable>args</replaceable> and the optional "
"<replaceable>range</replaceable>. The returned <replaceable>object</"
"replaceable> has a boolean property <replaceable>object.ok</replaceable> "
"that indicates whether execution of the <replaceable>command</replaceable> "
"was successful. In case of an error, the string <replaceable>object.status</"
"replaceable> contains an error message."
msgstr ""
"निष्पादयति<link linkend=\"advanced-editing-tools-commandline\"> आदेशपङ्क्तिः "
"आदेशः</link><replaceable> आदेश</replaceable> वैकल्पिकतर्कैः सह<replaceable> अर्ग्स्</"
"replaceable> वैकल्पिकं च<replaceable> पङ्क्तिः</replaceable> . "
"प्रत्यागताः<replaceable> वस्तु</replaceable> बूलियन गुणः अस्ति<replaceable> object."
"ok</replaceable> तत् सूचयति यत् निष्पादनं वा<replaceable> आदेश</replaceable> सफलः "
"अभवत् । दोषस्य सति स्ट्रिंग्<replaceable> वस्तु।स्थिति</replaceable> त्रुटिसन्देशः अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3224 development.docbook:3946 development.docbook:3956
#: development.docbook:3966
#, no-c-format
msgid "Since: &kde-frameworks; 5.50"
msgstr "यतः: &kde-frameworks; ५.५० इति"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Range view.searchText(<parameter>Range <replaceable>range</replaceable></"
"parameter>,\n"
"                      <parameter>String <replaceable>pattern</replaceable></"
"parameter>,\n"
"                      <parameter>bool <replaceable>backwards</replaceable> = "
"false</parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"Range view.searchText(<पैरामीटर>परिधि <प्रतिस्थापनीय>परिधि</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>,\n"
"                      <parameter>String <प्रतिस्थापनीय>प्रतिरूप</replaceable></"
"parameter>, .\n"
"                      <parameter>bool <प्रतिस्थापनीय>पश्चात्</replaceable> = "
"मिथ्या</parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Search for the first occurrence of <replaceable>pattern</replaceable> in "
"<replaceable>range</replaceable> and returns the matched range. Search is "
"performed backwards if the optional boolean parameter "
"<replaceable>backwards</replaceable> is set to <literal>true</literal>."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>pattern</replaceable> इत्यस्मिन् <replaceable>pattern</"
"replaceable> इत्यस्य प्रथमा आगमनं अन्वेष्टुम् अन्विष्य मेलयुक्तं परिधिं प्रत्यागच्छति । यदि "
"वैकल्पिकं बूलियन-पैरामीटर् <replaceable>backwards</replaceable> <literal>true</"
"literal> इति सेट् भवति तर्हि अन्वेषणं पश्चात् क्रियते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The returned range is invalid (see Range.isValid()) if <replaceable>pattern</"
"replaceable> is not found in <replaceable>range</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"यदि <replaceable>पैटर्न्</replaceable> <replaceable>range</replaceable> इत्यत्र न "
"लभ्यते तर्हि प्रत्यागतपरिधिः अमान्यः अस्ति (द्रष्टव्यम् Range.isValid()) ।"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3237
#, no-c-format
msgid "Since: &kde-frameworks; 5.97"
msgstr "यतः: &kde-frameworks; ५.९७ इति"

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:3246
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Document API"
msgstr "दस्तावेज एपिआइ इति"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whenever a script is being executed, there is a global variable "
"<quote><literal>document</literal></quote> representing the current active "
"document. The following is a list of all available Document functions."
msgstr ""
"यदा कदापि स्क्रिप्ट् निष्पादितं भवति तदा वर्तमानसक्रियदस्तावेजस्य प्रतिनिधित्वं कुर्वन् "
"वैश्विकचरः <quote><literal>दस्तावेज</literal></quote> भवति । निम्नलिखितम् सर्वेषां "
"उपलब्धानां Document कार्याणां सूची अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3255
#, no-c-format
msgid "String document.fileName();"
msgstr "String document.fileName ();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the document's filename or an empty string for unsaved text buffers."
msgstr "दस्तावेजस्य सञ्चिकानाम अथवा असरक्षितपाठबफरस्य कृते रिक्तं स्ट्रिंग् प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3263
#, no-c-format
msgid "String document.url();"
msgstr "स्ट्रिंग दस्तावेज़.url ();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the document's full &URL; or an empty string for unsaved text "
"buffers."
msgstr "दस्तावेजस्य पूर्णं &URL; अथवा असरक्षितपाठबफरस्य कृते रिक्तं स्ट्रिंग् ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3271
#, no-c-format
msgid "String document.mimeType();"
msgstr "स्ट्रिंग दस्तावेज़.mimeType ();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the document's &MIME; type or the &MIME; type <literal>application/"
"octet-stream</literal> if no appropriate &MIME; type could be found."
msgstr ""
"दस्तावेजस्य &MIME; प्रकारः अथवा &MIME; यदि उचितं नास्ति तर्हि <literal>application/"
"octet-stream</literal> इति टङ्कयन्तु &MIME; प्रकारः प्राप्यते स्म ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3280
#, no-c-format
msgid "String document.encoding();"
msgstr "String document.encoding ();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3281
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the currently used encoding to save the file."
msgstr "सञ्चिकां रक्षितुं वर्तमानकाले प्रयुक्तं एन्कोडिंग् प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3287
#, no-c-format
msgid "String document.highlightingMode();"
msgstr "String document.highlightingMode ();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3288
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the global highlighting mode used for the whole document."
msgstr "सम्पूर्णदस्तावेजस्य कृते प्रयुक्तं वैश्विकं हाइलाइटिङ्ग् मोड् प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.highlightingModeAt(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>pos</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.highlightingModeAt (<पैरामीटर> कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय>pos</"
"replaceable></पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the highlighting mode used at the given position in the document."
msgstr "दस्तावेजे दत्तस्थाने प्रयुक्तं हाइलाइटिङ्ग् मोड् प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3301
#, no-c-format
msgid "Array document.embeddedHighlightingModes();"
msgstr "सरणी document.embeddedHighlightingModes ();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3302
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns an array of highlighting modes embedded in this document."
msgstr "अस्मिन् दस्तावेजे निहितस्य हाइलाइटिङ्ग् मोड् इत्यस्य सरणीं प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3308
#, no-c-format
msgid "bool document.isModified();"
msgstr "bool दस्तावेज.isModified ();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3309
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the document has unsaved changes "
"(modified), otherwise <literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> इति प्रेषयति, यदि दस्तावेजे अरक्षिताः परिवर्तनाः (संशोधिताः) "
"सन्ति, अन्यथा <literal>false</literal> ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3316
#, no-c-format
msgid "String document.text();"
msgstr "स्ट्रिंग दस्तावेज़.पाठ ();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the entire content of the document in a single text string. Newlines "
"are marked with the newline character <quote><literal>\\n</literal></quote>."
msgstr ""
"दस्तावेजस्य सम्पूर्णं सामग्रीं एकस्मिन् पाठस्ट्रिंग् मध्ये प्रत्यागच्छति । नवीनपङ्क्तयः "
"<quote><literal>\\n</literal></quote> इति नूतनपङ्क्तिवर्णेन चिह्निताः भवन्ति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.text(<parameter>int <replaceable>fromLine</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>fromColumn</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>toLine</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>toColumn</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"String document.text(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>from</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>Cursor <replaceable>to</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"String document.text(<parameter>Range <replaceable>range</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.text(<parameter>int <replaceable>fromLine</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>fromColumn</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>toLine</replaceable इति स्ट्रिंग् ></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>स्तम्भं</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"String document.text(<पैरामीटर>कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय>तः</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय>तः</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"String document.text(<पैरामीटर>परिधि <प्रतिस्थापनीय>परिधि</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the text in the given range. It is recommended to use the cursor and "
"range based version for better readability of the source code."
msgstr ""
"दत्तपरिधिमध्ये पाठं प्रत्यागच्छति । स्रोतसङ्केतस्य उत्तमपठनीयतायै कर्सर-रेन्ज-आधारित-संस्करणस्य "
"उपयोगः अनुशंसितः ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.line(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.line(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3335
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the given text line as string. The string is empty if the requested "
"line is out of range."
msgstr ""
"दत्तां पाठपङ्क्तिं स्ट्रिंग् इति रूपेण प्रत्यागच्छति । यदि अनुरोधिता रेखा परिधितः बहिः अस्ति "
"तर्हि स्ट्रिंग् रिक्तं भवति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.wordAt(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"String document.wordAt(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.wordAt(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>, <पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>स्तम्भ</प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);\n"
"String document.wordAt (<पैरामीटर>कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय>कर्सर</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3344
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the word at the given cursor position."
msgstr "दत्तकर्सरस्थाने शब्दं प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3352
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Range document.wordRangeAt(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"Range document.wordRangeAt(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"Range document.wordRangeAt(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>स्तम्भ</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"Range document.wordRangeAt (<पैरामीटर> कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय> कर्सर</replaceable></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Return the range of the word at the given cursor position. The returned "
"range is invalid (see Range.isValid()), if the text position is after the "
"end of a line. If there is no word at the given cursor, an empty range is "
"returned."
msgstr ""
"दत्तकर्सरस्थाने शब्दस्य परिधिं प्रत्यागच्छतु । प्रत्यागतं परिधिः अमान्यः अस्ति (द्रष्टव्यम् "
"Range.isValid()), यदि पाठस्थानं पङ्क्तिसमाप्तेः अनन्तरं भवति । यदि दत्तकर्सरे शब्दः "
"नास्ति तर्हि रिक्तपरिधिः प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.charAt(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"String document.charAt(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.charAt(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>, <पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>स्तम्भ</प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);\n"
"String document.charAt (<पैरामीटर> कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय> कर्सर</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3368
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the character at the given cursor position."
msgstr "दत्तकर्सरस्थाने वर्णं प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.firstChar(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.firstChar (<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the first character in the given <replaceable>line</replaceable> "
"that is not a whitespace. The first character is at column 0. If the line is "
"empty or only contains whitespace characters, the returned string is empty."
msgstr ""
"दत्ते <replaceable>रेखायां</replaceable> प्रथमं वर्णं प्रत्यागच्छति यत् श्वेतस्थानं नास्ति । "
"प्रथमः वर्णः स्तम्भे 0. यदि रेखा रिक्तः अस्ति अथवा केवलं श्वेतस्थानवर्णाः सन्ति तर्हि "
"प्रत्यागतं स्ट्रिंग् रिक्तं भवति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3386
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.lastChar(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.lastChar (<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3387
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the last character in the given <replaceable>line</replaceable> that "
"is not a whitespace. If the line is empty or only contains whitespace "
"characters, the returned string is empty."
msgstr ""
"दत्ते <replaceable>रेखा</replaceable> मध्ये अन्तिमं वर्णं प्रत्यागच्छति यत् श्वेतस्थानं नास्ति "
"। यदि रेखा रिक्तं भवति अथवा केवलं श्वेतस्थानवर्णाः सन्ति तर्हि प्रत्यागतं स्ट्रिंग् रिक्तं भवति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isSpace(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isSpace(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isSpace(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>स्तम्भ</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isSpace (<पैरामीटर>कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय>कर्सर</replaceable></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3397
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the character at the given cursor "
"position is a whitespace, otherwise <literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> इति प्रत्यागच्छति, यदि दत्ते कर्सरस्थाने वर्णः श्वेतस्थानम् अस्ति, "
"अन्यथा <literal>false</literal> ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3405
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.matchesAt(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.matchesAt(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.matchesAt(<parameter>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>स्तम्भ</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>String <replaceable>पाठ</replaceable ></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.matchesAt(<पैरामीटर>कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय>कर्सर</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <पैरामीटर>स्ट्रिंग <प्रतिस्थापनीय>पाठ</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3406
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the given <replaceable>text</"
"replaceable> matches at the corresponding cursor position, otherwise "
"<literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> इति प्रत्यागच्छति, यदि दत्तः <replaceable>text</"
"replaceable> तत्सम्बद्धे कर्सरस्थाने मेलनं करोति, अन्यथा <literal>false</literal> ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3414
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.startsWith(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>bool <replaceable>skipWhiteSpaces</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.startsWith(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>स्ट्रिंग् <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>bool <replaceable>skipWhiteSpaces</replaceable इति ></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3415
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the line starts with <replaceable>text</"
"replaceable>, otherwise <literal>false</literal>. The argument "
"<replaceable>skipWhiteSpaces</replaceable> controls whether leading "
"whitespaces are ignored."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> इति प्रेषयति, यदि रेखा <replaceable>text</replaceable> "
"इत्यनेन आरभ्यते, अन्यथा <literal>false</literal> इति । "
"<replaceable>skipWhiteSpaces</replaceable> इति तर्कः अग्रणी श्वेतस्थानानि "
"उपेक्षितानि वा इति नियन्त्रयति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3423
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.endsWith(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>bool <replaceable>skipWhiteSpaces</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.endsWith(<parameter>int <replaceable>रेखा</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>स्ट्रिंग् <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>bool <replaceable>skipWhiteSpaces</replaceable इति ></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3424
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the line ends with <replaceable>text</"
"replaceable>, otherwise <literal>false</literal>. The argument "
"<replaceable>skipWhiteSpaces</replaceable> controls whether trailing "
"whitespaces are ignored."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> इति प्रत्यागच्छति, यदि पङ्क्तिः <replaceable>text</"
"replaceable> इत्यनेन समाप्तं भवति, अन्यथा <literal>false</literal> इति । "
"<replaceable>skipWhiteSpaces</replaceable> इति तर्कः अनुवर्तमानशुक्लस्थानानि "
"उपेक्षितानि वा इति नियन्त्रयति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3432
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.setText(<parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.setText (<पैरामीटर>स्ट्रिंग <प्रतिस्थापनीय>पाठ</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3433
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sets the entire document text."
msgstr "सम्पूर्णं दस्तावेजपाठं सेट् करोति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3440
#, no-c-format
msgid "bool document.clear();"
msgstr "bool document.clear ();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3441
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removes the entire text in the document."
msgstr "दस्तावेजे सम्पूर्णं पाठं निष्कासयति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3448
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.truncate(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.truncate(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.truncate(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>, <पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>स्तम्भ</प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);\n"
"bool document.truncate(<पैरामीटर>कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय>कर्सर</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Truncate the given line at the given column or cursor position. Returns "
"<literal>true</literal> on success, or <literal>false</literal> if the given "
"line is not part of the document range."
msgstr ""
"दत्तां स्तम्भे अथवा कर्सरस्थाने दत्तां रेखां च्छेदयन्तु । सफलतायां <literal>true</literal> "
"प्रत्यागच्छति, अथवा <literal>false</literal> यदि दत्ता रेखा दस्तावेजपरिधिभागः नास्ति "
"।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3457
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.insertText(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.insertText(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.insertText(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>स्तम्भ</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>स्ट्रिंग् <प्रतिस्थापनीय>पाठ</replaceable ></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.insertText(<पैरामीटर>कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय>कर्सर</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <पैरामीटर>स्ट्रिंग <प्रतिस्थापनीय>पाठ</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3458
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inserts the <replaceable>text</replaceable> at the given cursor position. "
"Returns <literal>true</literal> on success, or <literal>false</literal>, if "
"the document is in read-only mode."
msgstr ""
"दत्ते कर्सरस्थाने <replaceable>text</replaceable> निवेशयति । सफलतायां "
"<literal>true</literal>, अथवा <literal>false</literal>, यदि दस्तावेजः केवलं "
"पठनीयविधाने अस्ति तर्हि प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3466
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.removeText(<parameter>int <replaceable>fromLine</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>fromColumn</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>toLine</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>toColumn</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.removeText(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>from</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>Cursor <replaceable>to</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.removeText(<parameter>Range <replaceable>range</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.removeText(<पैरामीटर>int <replaceable>fromLine</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>fromColumn</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>toLine</replaceable इति ></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>स्तम्भं</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.removeText(<पैरामीटर>कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय>तः</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <पैरामीटर>कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय>तः</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.removeText (<पैरामीटर>परिधि <प्रतिस्थापनीय>परिधि</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3467
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Removes the text in the given range. Returns <literal>true</literal> on "
"success, or <literal>false</literal>, if the document is in read-only mode."
msgstr ""
"दत्तपरिधिस्थं पाठं निष्कासयति । सफलतायां <literal>true</literal>, अथवा "
"<literal>false</literal>, यदि दस्तावेजः केवलं पठनीयविधाने अस्ति तर्हि प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3475
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.insertLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.insertLine(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>, <पैरामीटर>स्ट्रिंग <प्रतिस्थापनीय>पाठ</प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3476
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inserts text in the given line. Returns <literal>true</literal> on success, "
"or <literal>false</literal>, if the document is in read-only mode or the "
"line is not in the document range."
msgstr ""
"दत्तपङ्क्तौ पाठं निवेशयति । सफलतायां <literal>true</literal>, अथवा <literal>false</"
"literal>, यदि दस्तावेजः केवलं पठनीयविधाने अस्ति अथवा रेखा दस्तावेजपरिधिषु नास्ति तर्हि "
"प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3484
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.removeLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.removeLine (<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3485
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Removes the given text line. Returns <literal>true</literal> on success, or "
"<literal>false</literal>, if the document is in read-only mode or the line "
"is not in the document range."
msgstr ""
"दत्तां पाठपङ्क्तिं निष्कासयति । सफलतायां <literal>true</literal>, अथवा "
"<literal>false</literal>, यदि दस्तावेजः केवलं पठनीयविधाने अस्ति अथवा रेखा "
"दस्तावेजपरिधिषु नास्ति तर्हि प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3493
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.wrapLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.wrapLine(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.wrapLine(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>, <पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>स्तम्भ</प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);\n"
"bool document.wrapLine (<पैरामीटर> कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय> कर्सर</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3494
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Wraps the line at the given cursor position. Returns <literal>true</literal> "
"on success, otherwise <literal>false</literal>, &eg; if line &lt; 0."
msgstr ""
"दत्तकर्सरस्थाने रेखां वेष्टयति । सफलतायां <literal>true</literal> प्रत्यागच्छति, अन्यथा "
"<literal>false</literal>, &eg; यदि रेखा &lt; ० ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3506
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void document.joinLines(<parameter>int <replaceable>startLine</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>endLine</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"void document.joinLines(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>प्रारम्भरेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>, <पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>अन्तरेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3507
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Joins the lines from <replaceable>startLine</replaceable> to "
"<replaceable>endLine</replaceable>. Two succeeding text lines are always "
"separated with a single space."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>startLine</replaceable> तः <replaceable>endLine</replaceable> "
"पर्यन्तं पङ्क्तयः संयोजयति । द्वौ क्रमिकौ पाठरेखाद्वयं सर्वदा एकेन रिक्तस्थानेन विभक्तौ भवतः ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3515
#, no-c-format
msgid "int document.lines();"
msgstr "int दस्तावेज़.रेखा ();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3516
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the number of lines in the document."
msgstr "दस्तावेजे पङ्क्तयः संख्यां प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3523
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isLineModified(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isLineModified (<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3524
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if <replaceable>line</replaceable> "
"currently contains unsaved data."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> इति प्रत्यागच्छति, यदि <replaceable>line</replaceable> "
"इत्यत्र सम्प्रति अरक्षितदत्तांशः अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3527 development.docbook:3539 development.docbook:3550
#: development.docbook:3562 development.docbook:3736
#, no-c-format
msgid "Since: &kde; 5.0"
msgstr "यतः: &where; ५.० इति"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3534
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isLineSaved(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isLineSaved (<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3535
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if <replaceable>line</replaceable> was "
"changed, but the document was saved. Hence, the line currently does not "
"contain any unsaved data."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> इति प्रेषयति, यदि <replaceable>line</replaceable> "
"परिवर्तिता, परन्तु दस्तावेजं रक्षितम् । अतः, रेखायां सम्प्रति किमपि असरक्षितं दत्तांशं नास्ति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3546
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isLineTouched(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isLineTouched(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3547
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if <replaceable>line</replaceable> "
"currently contains unsaved data or was changed before."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> इति प्रत्यागच्छति, यदि <replaceable>line</replaceable> "
"इत्यत्र सम्प्रति अरक्षितदत्तांशः अस्ति अथवा पूर्वं परिवर्तितः अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3557
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.findTouchedLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>startLine</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>bool <replaceable>down</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.findTouchedLine(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>प्रारम्भरेखा</"
"प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>, <पैरामीटर>bool <प्रतिस्थापनीय>अधः</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3558
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Search for the next touched line starting at <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable>. The search is performed either upwards or downwards depending "
"on the search direction specified in <replaceable>down</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>line</replaceable> इत्यस्मात् आरभ्य अग्रिमस्पृष्टां रेखां अन्वेष्टुम् । "
"<replaceable>down</replaceable> इत्यत्र निर्दिष्टा अन्वेषणदिशानुसारं अन्वेषणं ऊर्ध्वं अधः "
"वा क्रियते ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3569
#, no-c-format
msgid "int document.length();"
msgstr "int दस्तावेज़.दीर्घता ();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3570
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the number of characters in the document."
msgstr "दस्तावेजे वर्णानाम् संख्यां प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3577
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.lineLength(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.lineLength (<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3578
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the <replaceable>line</replaceable>'s length."
msgstr "<replaceable>रेखा</replaceable> इत्यस्य दीर्घतां प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3585
#, no-c-format
msgid "void document.editBegin();"
msgstr "void document.editBegin ();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3586
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Starts an edit group for undo/redo grouping. Make sure to always call "
"<function>editEnd()</function> as often as you call <function>editBegin()</"
"function>. Calling <function>editBegin()</function> internally uses a "
"reference counter, &ie;, this call can be nested."
msgstr ""
"पूर्ववत/पुनः करणं समूहीकरणाय सम्पादनसमूहं आरभते । यथावारं <function>editBegin()</"
"function> इति आह्वयन्ति तथा सर्वदा <function>editEnd()</function> इति आह्वयितुं "
"सुनिश्चितं कुर्वन्तु । <function>editBegin()</function> इति आह्वानं आन्तरिकरूपेण "
"सन्दर्भगणकस्य उपयोगं करोति, &ie;, एतत् आह्वानं नेस्ट् कर्तुं शक्यते ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3596
#, no-c-format
msgid "void document.editEnd();"
msgstr "void दस्तावेज़.संपादन समाप्त ();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3597
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Ends an edit group. The last call of <function>editEnd()</function> (&ie; "
"the one for the first call of <function>editBegin()</function>) finishes the "
"edit step."
msgstr ""
"सम्पादनसमूहस्य समाप्तिः भवति । <function>editEnd()</function> इत्यस्य अन्तिमः "
"आह्वानः (&अर्थात् <function>editBegin()</function> इत्यस्य प्रथमस्य आह्वानस्य कृते यः) "
"सम्पादनपदं समाप्तं करोति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3606
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.firstColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.firstColumn (<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3607
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the first non-whitespace column in the given <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable>. If there are only whitespaces in the line, the return value is "
"<literal>-1</literal>."
msgstr ""
"दत्ते <replaceable>रेखा</replaceable> मध्ये प्रथमं अश्वेतस्थानस्तम्भं प्रत्यागच्छति । यदि "
"पङ्क्तौ केवलं श्वेतस्थानानि सन्ति तर्हि प्रत्यागमनमूल्यं <literal>-1</literal> भवति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3615
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.lastColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.lastColumn (<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3616
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the last non-whitespace column in the given <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable>. If there are only whitespaces in the line, the return value is "
"<literal>-1</literal>."
msgstr ""
"दत्ते <replaceable>रेखा</replaceable> मध्ये अन्तिमं अश्वेतस्थानस्तम्भं प्रत्यागच्छति । यदि "
"पङ्क्तौ केवलं श्वेतस्थानानि सन्ति तर्हि प्रत्यागमनमूल्यं <literal>-1</literal> भवति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3624
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.prevNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"int document.prevNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.prevNonSpaceColumn(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>स्तम्भ</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"int document.prevNonSpaceColumn (<पैरामीटर> कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय> कर्सर</"
"प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3625
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the column with a non-whitespace character starting at the given "
"cursor position and searching backwards."
msgstr "दत्तकर्सरस्थानात् आरभ्य पश्चात् अन्वेषणं कृत्वा अश्वेतस्थानवर्णेन सह स्तम्भं प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3633
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.nextNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"int document.nextNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.nextNonSpaceColumn(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>, <पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>स्तम्भ</प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);\n"
"int document.nextNonSpaceColumn (<पैरामीटर> कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय> कर्सर</"
"प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3634
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the column with a non-whitespace character starting at the given "
"cursor position and searching forwards."
msgstr "दत्तकर्सरस्थानात् आरभ्य अग्रे अन्वेषणं कृत्वा अश्वेतस्थानवर्णेन सह स्तम्भं प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3642
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.prevNonEmptyLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.prevNonEmptyLine (<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3643
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the next non-empty line containing non-whitespace characters "
"searching backwards."
msgstr ""
"पश्चात् अन्वेषणं कुर्वन्तः अश्वेतस्थानवर्णाः समाविष्टाः अग्रिमा-रिक्तपङ्क्तिं प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3651
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.nextNonEmptyLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.nextNonEmptyLine (<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3652
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the next non-empty line containing non-whitespace characters "
"searching forwards."
msgstr "अग्रे अन्वेषणं कुर्वन्तः अश्वेतस्थानवर्णाः समाविष्टाः अग्रिमा-रिक्तपङ्क्तिं प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3660
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isInWord(<parameter>String <replaceable>character</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isInWord(<पैरामीटर>स्ट्रिंग <प्रतिस्थापनीय>वर्ण</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>गुण</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3661
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the given <replaceable>character</"
"replaceable> with the given <replaceable>attribute</replaceable> can be part "
"of a word, otherwise <literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> इति प्रत्यागच्छति, यदि दत्तेन <replaceable>attribute</"
"replaceable> इत्यनेन सह दत्तः <replaceable>वर्णः</replaceable> शब्दस्य भागः भवितुम् "
"अर्हति, अन्यथा <literal>false</literal> ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3670
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.canBreakAt(<parameter>String <replaceable>character</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.canBreakAt(<पैरामीटर>स्ट्रिंग <प्रतिस्थापनीय>वर्ण</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>गुण</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3671
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the given <replaceable>character</"
"replaceable> with the given <replaceable>attribute</replaceable> is suited "
"to wrap a line, otherwise <literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> इति प्रत्यागच्छति, यदि दत्तेन <replaceable>attribute</"
"replaceable> इत्यनेन सह दत्तः <replaceable>वर्णः</replaceable> रेखां वेष्टयितुं उपयुक्तः "
"अस्ति, अन्यथा <literal>false</literal> ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3680
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.canComment(<parameter>int <replaceable>startAttribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>endAttribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.canComment(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>प्रारंभगुण</replaceable></"
"पैरामीटर>, <पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>अन्तगुण</प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3681
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if a range starting and ending with the "
"given attributes is suited to be commented out, otherwise <literal>false</"
"literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> इति प्रत्यागच्छति, यदि दत्तविशेषणैः आरभ्यमाणः परिधिः टिप्पणीं "
"कर्तुं उपयुक्तः अस्ति, अन्यथा <literal>false</literal> ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3689
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.commentMarker(<parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.commentMarker (<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>विशेषता</"
"प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3690
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the comment marker for single line comments for a given "
"<replaceable>attribute</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"दत्तस्य <replaceable>गुण</replaceable> कृते एकपङ्क्तिटिप्पणीनां कृते टिप्पणीचिह्नं "
"प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3697
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.commentStart(<parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.commentStart (<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>विशेषता</"
"प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3698
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the comment marker for the start of multi-line comments for a given "
"<replaceable>attribute</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"दत्तस्य <replaceable>विशेषणस्य</replaceable> कृते बहुपङ्क्तिटिप्पणीनां आरम्भार्थं "
"टिप्पणीचिह्नं प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3706
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.commentEnd(<parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.commentEnd (<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>गुण</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3707
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the comment marker for the end of multi-line comments for a given "
"<replaceable>attribute</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"दत्तस्य <replaceable>विशेषणस्य</replaceable> कृते बहुपङ्क्तिटिप्पणीनां समाप्त्यर्थं "
"टिप्पणीचिह्नं प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3715
#, no-c-format
msgid "Range document.documentRange();"
msgstr "श्रेणी document.documentRange ();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3716
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns a range that encompasses the whole document."
msgstr "एकं परिधिं प्रत्यागच्छति यत् सम्पूर्णं दस्तावेजं व्याप्नोति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3723
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cursor documentEnd();"
msgstr "कर्सर documentEnd ();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3724
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns a cursor positioned at the last column of the last line in the "
"document."
msgstr "दस्तावेजे अन्तिमपङ्क्तौ अन्तिमस्तम्भे स्थितं कर्सरं प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3731
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool isValidTextPosition(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool isValidTextPosition(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool isValidTextPosition(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>स्तम्भ</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool isValidTextPosition(<पैरामीटर> कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय> कर्सर</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3732
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the given cursor position is positioned "
"at a valid text position. A text position is valid only if it locate at the "
"start, in the middle, or the end of a valid line. Further, a text position "
"is invalid if it is located in a Unicode surrogate."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> इति प्रेषयति, यदि दत्तं कर्सरस्थानं वैधपाठस्थाने स्थितम् अस्ति । "
"पाठस्थानं तदा एव मान्यं भवति यदा सः वैधपङ्क्तिः आरम्भे, मध्ये, अन्ते वा स्थापयति । ततः परं, "
"यदि पाठस्थानं यूनिकोड-प्रतिनिधिस्थाने स्थितम् अस्ति तर्हि अमान्यं भवति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3743
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.attribute(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"int document.attribute(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.attribute(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>, <पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>स्तम्भ</प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);\n"
"int document.attribute(<पैरामीटर>कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय>कर्सर</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3744
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the attribute at the given cursor position."
msgstr "दत्तकर्सरस्थाने विशेषतां प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3751
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isAttribute(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isAttribute(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isAttribute(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>स्तम्भ</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>गुण</replaceable ></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isAttribute(<पैरामीटर>कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय>कर्सर</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>गुण</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3752
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the attribute at the given cursor "
"position equals <replaceable>attribute</replaceable>, otherwise "
"<literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> प्रत्यागच्छति, यदि दत्तकर्सरस्थाने विशेषता "
"<replaceable>attribute</replaceable> इत्यस्य बराबरं भवति, अन्यथा <literal>false</"
"literal> ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3760
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.attributeName(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"String document.attributeName(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.attributeName(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>, <पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>स्तम्भ</प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);\n"
"String document.attributeName (<पैरामीटर> कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय> कर्सर</"
"प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3761
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the attribute name as human readable text. This is equal to the "
"<literal>itemData</literal> name in the syntax highlighting files."
msgstr ""
"विशेषतानाम मानवपठनीयपाठरूपेण प्रत्यागच्छति । इदं वाक्यविन्यासप्रकाशनसञ्चिकासु "
"<literal>itemData</literal> इति नाम्नः तुल्यम् अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3769
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isAttributeName(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>name</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isAttributeName(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>name</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isAttributeName(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>स्तम्भ</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>स्ट्रिंग् <replaceable>नाम</replaceable ></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isAttributeName(<पैरामीटर>कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय>कर्सर</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <पैरामीटर>स्ट्रिंग <प्रतिस्थापनीय>नाम</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3770
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the attribute name at a certain cursor "
"position matches the given <replaceable>name</replaceable>, otherwise "
"<literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> इति प्रेषयति, यदि कस्मिंश्चित् कर्सरस्थाने विशेषतानाम दत्तेन "
"<replaceable>name</replaceable> इत्यनेन सह मेलनं करोति, अन्यथा <literal>false</"
"literal> ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3778
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.variable(<parameter>String <replaceable>key</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.variable (<पैरामीटर>स्ट्रिंग <प्रतिस्थापनीय>कुंजी</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3779
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the value of the requested document variable <replaceable>key</"
"replaceable>. If the document variable does not exist, the return value is "
"an empty string."
msgstr ""
"अनुरोधितस्य दस्तावेजचरस्य <replaceable>key</replaceable> इत्यस्य मूल्यं प्रत्यागच्छति । "
"यदि document variable नास्ति तर्हि return value रिक्तं स्ट्रिंग् भवति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3787
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void document.setVariable(<parameter>String <replaceable>key</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>value</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"void document.setVariable(<पैरामीटर>स्ट्रिंग <प्रतिस्थापनीय>कुंजी</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <पैरामीटर>स्ट्रिंग <प्रतिस्थापनीय>मूल्य</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3788
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the value of the requested document variable <replaceable>key</"
"replaceable>."
msgstr "अनुरोधितदस्तावेजचरस्य मूल्यं <replaceable>key</replaceable> इति सेट् कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3791
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See also: <link linkend=\"config-variables\">Kate document variables</link>"
msgstr ""
"इदमपि पश्यन्तु : १.<link linkend=\"config-variables\"> केट दस्तावेज चर</link>"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3794
#, no-c-format
msgid "Since: &kde; 4.8"
msgstr "यतः: &where; ४.८"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3801
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.firstVirtualColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.firstVirtualColumn (<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</"
"प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3802
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the virtual column of the first non-whitespace character in the "
"given line or <literal>-1</literal>, if the line is empty or contains only "
"whitespace characters."
msgstr ""
"दत्तपङ्क्तौ प्रथमस्य अश्वेतस्थानवर्णस्य आभासीस्तम्भं प्रत्यागच्छति अथवा <literal>-1</"
"literal>, यदि रेखा रिक्तं भवति अथवा केवलं श्वेतस्थानवर्णाः सन्ति"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3810
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.lastVirtualColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.lastVirtualColumn (<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3811
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the virtual column of the last non-whitespace character in the given "
"line or <literal>-1</literal>, if the line is empty or contains only "
"whitespace characters."
msgstr ""
"दत्तपङ्क्तौ अन्तिमस्य अश्वेतस्थानवर्णस्य आभासीस्तम्भं प्रत्यागच्छति अथवा <literal>-1</"
"literal>, यदि रेखा रिक्तं भवति अथवा केवलं श्वेतस्थानवर्णाः सन्ति"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3819
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.toVirtualColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"int document.toVirtualColumn(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"Cursor document.toVirtualCursor(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.toVirtualColumn(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</replaceable></"
"पैरामीटर>, <पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>स्तम्भ</replaceable></पैरामीटर>);\n"
"int document.toVirtualColumn (<पैरामीटर> कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय> कर्सर</"
"प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);\n"
"कर्सर document.toVirtualCursor(<पैरामीटर>कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय>कर्सर</replaceable></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3820
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Converts the given <quote>real</quote> cursor position to a virtual cursor "
"position, either returning an int or a Cursor object."
msgstr ""
"दत्तं <quote>real</quote> कर्सरस्थानं वर्चुअल् कर्सरस्थानं प्रति परिवर्तयति, int अथवा "
"Cursor ऑब्जेक्ट् प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3828
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.fromVirtualColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>virtualColumn</"
"replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"int document.fromVirtualColumn(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>virtualCursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"Cursor document.fromVirtualCursor(<parameter>Cursor "
"<replaceable>virtualCursor</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.fromVirtualColumn(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</replaceable></"
"पैरामीटर>, <पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>आभासीस्तम्भ</replaceable></पैरामीटर>);\n"
"int document.fromVirtualColumn (<पैरामीटर> कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय> आभासी कर्सर</"
"प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);\n"
"कर्सर document.fromVirtualCursor(<पैरामीटर>कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय>आभासीकर्सर</"
"प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3829
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Converts the given virtual cursor position to a <quote>real</quote> cursor "
"position, either returning an int or a Cursor object."
msgstr ""
"दत्तं वर्चुअल् कर्सरस्थानं <quote>real</quote> कर्सरस्थानं प्रति परिवर्तयति, int अथवा "
"Cursor ऑब्जेक्ट् प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3837
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Cursor document.anchor(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>Char <replaceable>character</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"Cursor document.anchor(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>Char <replaceable>character</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"कर्सर document.anchor(<parameter>int <replaceable>रेखा</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>स्तम्भ</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>Char <replaceable>वर्ण</replaceable ></parameter>);\n"
"कर्सर document.anchor(<पैरामीटर>कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय>कर्सर</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <पैरामीटर>चर <प्रतिस्थापनीय>वर्ण</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3838
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Searches backward for the given character starting from the given cursor. As "
"an example, if '(' is passed as character, this function will return the "
"position of the opening '('. This reference counting, &ie; other '(...)' are "
"ignored."
msgstr ""
"दत्तकर्सरतः आरभ्य दत्तं वर्णं पृष्ठतः अन्वेषयति । उदाहरणरूपेण यदि '(' वर्णरूपेण पारितं भवति "
"तर्हि एतत् फंक्शन् '(' उद्घाटनस्य स्थानं प्रत्यागमिष्यति। एतत् सन्दर्भगणना, &ie; अन्ये "
"'(...)' उपेक्षिताः भवन्ति।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3848
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Cursor document.rfind(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</replaceable> = -1</parameter>);\n"
"Cursor document.rfind(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</replaceable> = -1</parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"कर्सर document.rfind(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>स्तम्भ</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable इति ></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>गुण</प्रतिस्थापनीय> = -1</parameter>);\n"
"कर्सर document.rfind(<parameter>कर्सर <replaceable>कर्सर</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>गुणः</replaceable > = -1</पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3849
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Find searching backwards the given text with the appropriate "
"<replaceable>attribute</replaceable>. The argument <replaceable>attribute</"
"replaceable> is ignored if it is set to <literal>-1</literal>. The returned "
"cursor is invalid, if the text could not be found."
msgstr ""
"दत्तं पाठं पृष्ठतः अन्वेषणं समुचितेन <replaceable>attribute</replaceable> इत्यनेन सह "
"अन्वेष्टुम् । <replaceable>attribute</replaceable> इति तर्कः <literal>-1</literal> "
"इति सेट् कृतः चेत् उपेक्षितः भवति । प्रत्यागतः कर्सरः अमान्यः अस्ति, यदि पाठः न लब्धः ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3858
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.defStyleNum(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"int document.defStyleNum(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.defStyleNum(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>स्तम्भ</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"int document.defStyleNum (<पैरामीटर> कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय> कर्सर</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3859
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the default style used at the given cursor position."
msgstr "दत्तकर्सरस्थाने प्रयुक्तां पूर्वनिर्धारितशैलीं प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3866
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isCode(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isCode(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isCode(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>स्तम्भ</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isCode (<पैरामीटर> कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय>कर्सर</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3867
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the attribute at the given cursor "
"position is not equal to all of the following styles: <literal>dsComment</"
"literal>, <literal>dsString</literal>, <literal>dsRegionMarker</literal>, "
"<literal>dsChar</literal>, <literal>dsOthers</literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> प्रत्यागच्छति, यदि दत्तकर्सरस्थाने विशेषता निम्नलिखितशैल्याः "
"सर्वैः समानं नास्ति: <literal>dsComment</literal>, <literal>dsString</literal>, "
"<literal>dsRegionMarker </literal>, <literal>dsChar</literal>, "
"<literal>dsअन्य</literal> इति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3878
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isComment(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isComment(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isComment(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>स्तम्भ</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isComment(<पैरामीटर>कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय>कर्सर</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3879
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the attribute of the character at the "
"cursor position is <literal>dsComment</literal>, otherwise <literal>false</"
"literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> इति प्रेषयति, यदि कर्सरस्थाने वर्णस्य विशेषता "
"<literal>dsComment</literal> अस्ति, अन्यथा <literal>false</literal> ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3887
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isString(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isString(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isString(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>, <पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>स्तम्भ</प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);\n"
"bool document.isString (<पैरामीटर> कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय>कर्सर</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3888
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the attribute of the character at the "
"cursor position is <literal>dsString</literal>, otherwise <literal>false</"
"literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> इति प्रत्यागच्छति, यदि कर्सरस्थाने वर्णस्य विशेषता "
"<literal>dsString</literal> अस्ति, अन्यथा <literal>false</literal> ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3896
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isRegionMarker(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isRegionMarker(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isRegionMarker(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>, <पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>स्तम्भ</प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);\n"
"bool document.isRegionMarker (<पैरामीटर> कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय> कर्सर</"
"प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3897
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the attribute of the character at the "
"cursor position is <literal>dsRegionMarker</literal>, otherwise "
"<literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> इति प्रेषयति, यदि कर्सरस्थाने वर्णस्य विशेषता "
"<literal>dsRegionMarker</literal> अस्ति, अन्यथा <literal>false</literal> ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3905
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isChar(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isChar(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isChar(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>, "
"<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>स्तम्भ</प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);\n"
"bool document.isChar (<पैरामीटर> कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय>कर्सर</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3906
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the attribute of the character at the "
"cursor position is <literal>dsChar</literal>, otherwise <literal>false</"
"literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> इति प्रत्यागच्छति, यदि कर्सरस्थाने वर्णस्य विशेषता "
"<literal>dsChar</literal> अस्ति, अन्यथा <literal>false</literal> ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3914
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isOthers(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isOthers(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isOthers(<पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>रेखा</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>, <पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>स्तम्भ</प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);\n"
"bool document.isOthers(<पैरामीटर>कर्सर <प्रतिस्थापनीय>कर्सर</replaceable></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3915
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the attribute of the character at the "
"cursor position is <literal>dsOthers</literal>, otherwise <literal>false</"
"literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>true</literal> इति प्रत्यागच्छति, यदि कर्सरस्थाने वर्णस्य विशेषता "
"<literal>dsOthers</literal> अस्ति, अन्यथा <literal>false</literal> ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3922
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void document.indent(<parameter>Range <replaceable>range</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>change</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"void document.indent(<पैरामीटर>परिधि <प्रतिस्थापनीय>परिधि</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>, <पैरामीटर>int <प्रतिस्थापनीय>परिवर्तन</प्रतिस्थापनीय></पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3923
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Indents all lines in <replaceable>range</replaceable> by "
"<replaceable>change</replaceable> tabs or <replaceable>change</replaceable> "
"times <literal>tabSize</literal> spaces depending on the users preferences. "
"The <replaceable>change</replaceable> parameter can be negative."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>range</replaceable> इत्यस्मिन् सर्वाणि पङ्क्तयः <replaceable>change</"
"replaceable> ट्याब् इत्यनेन अथवा <replaceable>change</replaceable> समयैः "
"<literal>tabSize</literal> रिक्तस्थानैः उपयोक्तृणां प्राधान्यानुसारं इन्डेण्ट् करोति । "
"<replaceable>change</replaceable> पैरामीटर् नकारात्मकं भवितुम् अर्हति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:3934
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Editor API"
msgstr "सम्पादक एपिआइ इति"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3935
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition to the document and view API, there is a general editor API that "
"provides functions for general editor scripting functionality."
msgstr ""
"दस्तावेजस्य दृश्यस्य च एपिआइ इत्यस्य अतिरिक्तं सामान्यसम्पादक एपिआइ अस्ति यत् "
"सामान्यसम्पादकस्क्रिप्टिङ्ग् कार्यक्षमतायाः कृते कार्याणि प्रदाति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3942
#, no-c-format
msgid "String editor.clipboardText();"
msgstr "स्ट्रिंग editor.clipboardText ();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3943
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the text that currently is in the global clipboard."
msgstr "वर्तमानकाले वैश्विकक्लिप्बोर्ड् मध्ये यत् पाठं वर्तते तत् प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3951
#, no-c-format
msgid "String editor.clipboardHistory();"
msgstr "स्ट्रिंग एडिटर.क्लिपबोर्डइतिहास ();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3952
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The editor holds a clipboard history that contains up to 10 clipboard "
"entries. This function returns all entries that currently are in the "
"clipboard history."
msgstr ""
"सम्पादकः क्लिप्बोर्ड् इतिहासं धारयति यस्मिन् १० क्लिप्बोर्ड् प्रविष्टयः यावत् सन्ति । एतत् "
"फंक्शन् सर्वाणि प्रविष्टयः प्रत्यागच्छति ये सम्प्रति क्लिप्बोर्ड् इतिहासे सन्ति ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3961
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void editor.setClipboardText(<parameter>String <replaceable>text</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"void editor.setClipboardText (<पैरामीटर>स्ट्रिंग <प्रतिस्थापनीय>पाठ</प्रतिस्थापनीय></"
"पैरामीटर>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3962
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the contents of the clipboard to <replaceable>text</replaceable>. The "
"<replaceable>text</replaceable> will be added to the clipboard history."
msgstr ""
"क्लिप्बोर्डस्य सामग्रीं <replaceable>text</replaceable> इति सेट् कुर्वन्तु । "
"<replaceable>text</replaceable> इति क्लिप्बोर्ड-इतिहासस्य मध्ये योजितं भविष्यति ।"
